posting_body: ['No broker fee', 'No amenity fee', 'Amazing NYC & River Views!', 'High Floor Illuminated Corner Two Bed Flex South Facing!', 'Light-Filled Rooms!', 'The apartment also has a beautiful open kitchen equipped w granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances as well as a dishwasher.', 'High Ceilings', 'Walls Allowed', 'Our World Class Amenities include 24 Doorman and concierge services as well as a virtual doorman system, an expansive courtyard on the lobby level, a state of the art fitness center, media room, children’s playroom, tenants lounge, bicycle storage, cold storage, package room, parking, outdoor dog run/park complete with dog washing station, a 9th Floor Terrace with Absolutely Stunning Views of the 59th Street Bridge, NYC Skyline, & LIC, in addition to an immense roof-deck complete with cabanas & reserve-able grilles with panoramic views of the NYC, Queens, and Brooklyn Skyline.', 'For more info or a pvt showing', 'Feel free to contact me at anytime']
